    "body": "This is a feature, the KDF is currently configured to use 256MB of memory: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/develop/crypto/key_store_passphrase.go#L88\n\nWe may lower this if it's a problem for people, but currently you can simply add more memory to your docker instance and it should work fine.\n",
